OL,3,CJersey Zoo to elect new Board of
OL,4,CTrustees members by end of year
OL,6,FBy the end of the year, Durrell
OL,7,FConservation Trust will have new
OL,8,Fmembers on its board which will make
OL,9,Fkey decisions and set the future
OL,10,Fagenda for Jersey Zoo.
OL,12,FThere are currently eight positions
OL,13,Favailable on the Board of Trustees -
OL,14,Fmembers of the charity will vote for
OL,15,Fthe candidates before the AGM in
OL,16,FDecember.
OL,18,FAn external HR company was brought in
OL,19,Fto "conduct an independent review of
OL,20,Fall applicants and a first round of
OL,21,Finterviews".
