OL,3,CJersey Zoo to elect new Board of
OL,4,CTrustees members by end of year
OL,6,FFrom this shortlist, a list of
OL,7,Frecommended candidates was finalised.
OL,9,FHowever, several former employees at
OL,10,Fthe zoo applied and did not even
OL,11,Freceive an interview for the roles.
OL,13,FThey include the zoo's former Director
OL,14,Fof Conservation Management, Quentin
OL,15,FBloxam, who worked there for 45 years.
OL,17,FThis meant he had to nominate himself
OL,18,Finstead.
