OL,3,CJersey Zoo to elect new Board of
OL,4,CTrustees members by end of year
OL,6,FQuentin says: "All the very highly
OL,7,Fqualified people that applied never
OL,8,Feven got far - same as me. They didn't
OL,9,Fget anywhere.
OL,11,F"And yet, they were so well-qualified
OL,12,Fwith a tremendous history of Durrell -
OL,13,Fboth in direct animal management,
OL,14,Ffield research, finance, and
OL,15,Fgovernance."
