OL,3,CJersey Zoo to elect new Board of
OL,4,CTrustees members by end of year
OL,6,FThe Chair of Durrell's trust, Matthew
OL,7,FHatchwell, made the preferred list but
OL,8,Fdid not have to do an interview as he
OL,9,Fsays he went through a similar process
OL,10,Fwhen he was elected to the board three
OL,11,Fyears ago.
OL,13,FHe tells ITV News: "All I can tell you
OL,14,Fis we provided the role descriptions
OL,15,Fto the HR company that carried out the
OL,16,Finterviews.
OL,18,F"They looked at the applications that
OL,19,Fwere submitted and they interviewed
OL,20,Fabout half of the candidates and that
OL,21,Fchoice was entirely theirs.
